HEADWORD: Toxicomania
<hw>Tox`i*co*ma"ni*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See.
<er>Toxic</er>, and <er>Mania</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
