<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>An insane desire for intoxicating
or poisonous drugs, as alcohol or opium.</def> <rj><au>B. W.
Richardson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Toxifera</ent>⟦br⟧
